m express and pciisa form factors crafco inc is an ergon company which manufactures pavement maintenance products and equipment including hot pour asphalt crack sealants tricor refining llc is owned by a partnership of ergon and san joaquin refining inc lion oil has been an affiliate of ergon since  and owns a refinery located near smackover crude oil field and in el dorado arkansas as of october  ergon had sold its remaining interest in lion oil to delek us holdings inc for approximately  million lamptonlove inc ergons subsidiary serves liquid petroleum gas lpg retail and wholesale customers across the midsouth referencesedit  bunge ergon team on miss ethanol plant st louis business journal may   retrieved march    external linksedit ergon website ergon petroleum specialties marketing division diversified technology inc website mississippi business journal mississippi  this mississippirelated article is a stub you can help wikipedia by expanding it v t e this article about a natural gas or petroleumrelated company is a stub you can help wikipedia by expanding it v t e retrieved from httpsenwikipediaorgwindexphptitleergonincoldid categories oil companies of the united statesprivately held companies based in mississippicompanies based in mississippicompanies based in jackson mississippivicksburg mississippimississippi stubspetroleum company stubshidden categories articles needing additional references from march all articles needing additional referencesall stub articles navigation menu personal tools not logged intalkcontributionscreate accountlog in namespaces article talk variants views read edit view history more search navigation main pagecontentsfeatured contentcurrent eventsrandom articledonate to wikipediawikipedia store interaction helpabout wikipediacommunity portalrecent changescontact page tools what links hererelated changesupload filespecial pagespermanent linkpage informationwikidata itemcite this page printexport create a bookdownload as pdfprintable 